---
title: Lobster-Filled Ravioli & Shrimp with Zucchini Ribbons
description: When tender ravioli are packed with fresh lobster and pillowy ricotta, then topped with succulent, seared shrimp, we call that a crustacean celebration! This divine dish is kicked up a notch with zucchini ribbons, a lemony cream sauce, and a sprinkle of Parmesan and fresh lemon zest. We won’t call you shellfish for licking the plate clean.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/620c1ec315295878ed2ab905-7b236691.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/lobster-filled-ravioli-shrimp-620c1ec315295878ed2ab905-1af8220d.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/lobster-filled-ravioli-and-shrimp-620c1ec315295878ed2ab905
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 900 kcal
  fat: 58 g
